{"tid":2335542,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"張韶涵中國商演 唱一半被拉下台離場 觀眾傻眼","createTime":"2020-12-22T03:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T04:04:31.000Z","uid":263409,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"af683472fa5d1b8feda77cea3aea14a72da03283","tid":2335542,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕藝人張韶涵近年將事業重心轉往中國，她近日在中國湖北進行商演時吸引大批人潮，不料卻傳出在演出一半時被提早請下台，據稱原因是演出造成交通癱瘓，當時甚至連話還沒說完就被工作人員強行拉走。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，張韶涵19日在中國湖北宜昌市興發商業廣場為開幕活動進行商演，當天在演出前現場就擠滿人潮，並造成車輛堵塞，張韶涵原本預定要演唱3首歌，但她在登台演唱《隱形的翅膀》、《歐若拉》兩首歌後，就突然接到工作人員通知必須立刻下台，她在錯愕之餘也只能立刻向觀眾道歉。<br />\n<br />\n根據網路流傳的影片顯示，當時張韶涵一臉錯愕，並趕忙對觀眾表示「我剛剛被通知交通癱瘓，所以我沒有辦法繼續站在舞台上，非常抱歉，我現在必須得下台。」由於先前的演唱中現場觀眾反應十分熱烈，甚至跟著一起大合唱，張韶涵一說完台下立刻群起嘩然，張韶涵雖然還想多說點什麼，不過一旁的工作人員不斷催促，她也只能邊鞠躬邊離開舞台。在影片中一旁的音控人員也傻眼，直呼「挖操」、「還沒唱完呢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3388305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3388305&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=a846ad56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3388305&h=50bab2ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3388305</a>"},{"pid":"4847f2e88b026860e57433c8734e780281df15cc","tid":2335542,"uid":263409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"中國式演唱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371ae810d47ca5e6e5fa8c196ea873790b1ae23a","tid":2335542,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"挖操<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bd3ff73e5018fe6806ff2b21c7d2b95f94e482","tid":2335542,"uid":263409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"樣衰衰咁落台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://h5.video.weibo.com/show/1034:4584694574940229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fh5.video.weibo.com%2Fshow%2F1034%3A4584694574940229&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=2535ad34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://h5.video.weibo.com/show/1034:4584694574940229</a>"},{"pid":"f2a39b3c24d729684fc06b8eb1e4b7cc40dd1736","tid":2335542,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:44:14.000Z","msg":"大陸任何人也可以突然消失的。"},{"pid":"ea643af993dbd1147410624e7b43fe8681dbf1dc","tid":2335542,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:44:29.000Z","msg":"人多成咁，有武肺一鍋熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ec9dd31210544bf48751d3955b51f5cb9828df","tid":2335542,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f2a39b3c24d729684fc06b8eb1e4b7cc40dd1736","tid":2335542,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:44:14.000Z","msg":"大陸任何人也可以突然消失的。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"韭菜人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34be0b5a1242505cf6c8971308b51524a47aa987","tid":2335542,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"押送犯人去刑場"},{"pid":"9284104569d7e8f6678e91a27e60e89e03418948","tid":2335542,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34be0b5a1242505cf6c8971308b51524a47aa987","tid":2335542,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"押送犯人去刑場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"完全體驗了何謂<br />\n「解決問題的方法就是解決提出(製造)問題的人」"},{"pid":"3b2abbdf82d26b114a07e600be830a918f25f709","tid":2335542,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"未過數？"}]}